title: Drakan: Order of the Flame Playthrough â€” Part 1
description: This is a game from my childhood and I love it. It's kind of a classic fantasy game, but it's just really well done and super fun to play. As much as I've played this game I've actually never even beaten it, so the end of this game will be blind. It's strange how many games I loved as a kid I never even finished...
